34
00:02:46,067 --> 00:02:48,934
- Good evening, Bishop Brougham.
- How are you, Stevens?

35
00:02:49,004 --> 00:02:51,564
Mrs. Hamilton is
in the drawing room, sir.

36
00:02:51,640 --> 00:02:53,574
Thank you.

37
00:03:01,550 --> 00:03:03,484
Well, Bishop Brougham.

38
00:03:04,920 --> 00:03:07,286
My dear Mrs. Hamilton,
I've come to tell you...

39
00:03:07,355 --> 00:03:10,188
- You've come to apologize, I trust.
- Exactly.

40
00:03:10,258 --> 00:03:13,227
Upon mature consideration,
my objections seem petty...

41
00:03:13,295 --> 00:03:15,456
compared with your generous gesture.

42
00:03:15,530 --> 00:03:18,693
- I'm very relieved. Sit down, Bishop.
- Thank you.

43
00:03:18,767 --> 00:03:21,930
What hurt me most was to think
that my instinct had betrayed me...

44
00:03:22,003 --> 00:03:24,767
