Will you bring a pair of my trousers
over to Mrs. Hamilton's house?

164
00:10:41,209 --> 00:10:44,576
What difference does it make?
Just bring me another pair of trousers.

165
00:10:44,645 --> 00:10:46,909
Thank you.

166
00:10:46,981 --> 00:10:50,314
I'm so sorry this has happened.

167
00:10:50,385 --> 00:10:52,945
If only I could contact Julia or Dudley.

168
00:10:53,021 --> 00:10:55,114
Don't be nervous, Bishop.

169
00:10:56,858 --> 00:10:58,689
Have a chair.

170
00:10:58,760 --> 00:11:00,694
Thank you, I have one.

171
