172
00:11:09,837 --> 00:11:13,068
Perhaps the meeting was
more important than he thought.

173
00:11:13,141 --> 00:11:15,075
I suppose.

174
00:11:15,943 --> 00:11:17,877
We'd better go home.

175
00:11:21,215 --> 00:11:23,183
Dudley, it's strange thing.

176
00:11:23,251 --> 00:11:25,185
What's strange?

177
00:11:25,253 --> 00:11:29,212
You make me feel as if everything
is going to be all right.

178
00:11:29,290 --> 00:11:31,622
- It could be if...
- If what?

179
00:11:33,194 --> 00:11:36,061
If people could only learn
to behave like human beings.

180
00:11:39,434 --> 00:11:41,026
Hey, taxi.

181
00:11:48,242 --> 00:11:49,607
Here's a cab.

182
